A few weeks ago I started dabbling in the crypto space.  Let me tell you, it’s a lot. Lol! I saw some things in the space that I loved, saw some things that I didn’t love. Like rug pulls, that is not something your boy DC could get down with. That actually sounds like being pinned on the cage by Khabib, it’s just doesn’t sound like fun. Then a buddy of mine told me about @ultrasafe.bsc. I was immediately drawn in by the fact that the token is 100% rug proof, which means what’s mine stays mine. I also really like the fact that they have an interactive community and future goals, those are all good signs for me!

Today, I am very proud to announce that I have become an ambassador for UltraSafe!! I feel like cryptocurrency is the wave of the future…and I’m not the only one. Stay tuned for more updates from me & the good folks at @ultrasafe.bsc - D.C 

#DCgoesDefi #UltraSafe #UltraDC #UltraSafeAmbassador

node.text: Hey guys I am so excited to be opening my @danielcormierwrestlingacademy we are accepting new members now. The classes are as low as 8 dollars a class. You can go to our website to register, for beginners join our Baby Hawks class and work your way all the way up to our competition team. We also have Peleton bikes, treadmills and weights for the adults!! Check the link in my bio to register. If you’re anywhere near gilroy come and wrestle with us , don’t care what school you go to, come and wrestle with us!!!!! 6901 Monterey road gilroy CA 95020 let’s go Guys ! Get signed up, you never know who you’ll see in the gym!
